# Base URL for static data assets (election JSON, vector tiles, geo files).
# Unset (the default) → assets are served from the app's own origin under /data,
# i.e. from public/. No change needed for local dev or a plain static deploy.
#
# To serve the heavy assets (tiles + full commune JSON) from a CDN / object
# store instead, point this at a root that mirrors the same `data/...` layout,
# with NO trailing slash. Example:
#   VITE_DATA_BASE_URL=https://cdn.example.com
# Then https://cdn.example.com/data/tiles/france-admin.pmtiles must resolve.
#
# VITE_DATA_BASE_URL=
